qas.question: What did Spain trade Florida for

answers.text: In 1763, Spain traded Florida to the Kingdom of Great Britain for control of Havana, Cuba

qas.question: Who did the Spanish take from Florida to Cuba

answers.text: Almost the entire Spanish population left, taking along most of the remaining indigenous population to Cuba

qas.question: What road did the British construct

answers.text: the King's Road connecting St. Augustine to Georgia
